text: Picture this: A miniature world filled with everyday human activities. At the center of it all is a bright green frog, clearly out of its natural habitat. It's not just any ordinary frog, though. This one has a befuddled yet endearing look on its face, and it's adorned with a pair of swim goggles resting tightly on its head. Traverse into its world as it is caught in a hilariously human situation, perhaps waiting for a bus or trying to sip a tiny latte at a cafe, further emphasizing its charming peculiarity.
